game.name: Princess Fashion Competition
game.description:
Wow! You are again going to take a chance to become a fashionista in just a few simple steps by exploring the awesome fashion world in this brand new girls game. This time there are five beautiful princesses you have to dress them up. Are you ready to put your intense fashion abilities to the test? Join Princess Fashion Competition and be prepared to help five gorgeous girls to create the jaw-dropping looks for this major fashion contest! You would have plenty of outfit choices to choose from. 

Your hard work will definitely pay off, so keep mixing and matching as many dresses and accessories as you can to allow them to compete for a place in the finals. Anna, Elsa, Snow White, Ladybug and Ariel are the five princesses who will compete with each other in the contest. Begin the dressing fun with Anna and dress her up with a red color outfit with a glittery top and pair it with a black necklace and a pair of classic shoes! 

Now select a blue top without sleeves and combine it with a short fitted denim skirt, a cute purple handbag, and a pair of matching brown ankle boots. Then move towards Snow White who will look fabulous in a blue dress with two pockets on the top, a pair of red sandals with heel, and a blue and pink color handbag. A pair of red high waist pants, white, orange and pink striped sweater, a long beaded necklace, and big shoes with high heels will be perfect for Ladybug. Dress up Ariel with a cherry red outfit with a glittery collar!
